1
00:00:06,125 --> 00:00:08,450
=Fireworks=

2
00:00:08,537 --> 00:00:11,112
=Episode 2=

3
00:00:36,975 --> 00:00:39,337
(I'm inside Jiang Zechen's body!)

4
00:00:39,520 --> 00:00:41,119
- (Our consciousnesses have merged?)
- (Our consciousnesses have merged?)

5
00:00:44,562 --> 00:00:45,642
What else could it be?

6
00:00:46,560 --> 00:00:48,280
(I need to get out of his body fast.)

7
00:00:49,800 --> 00:00:50,840
Just figure something out.

8
00:00:52,425 --> 00:00:53,359
(Consciousness space)

9
00:00:53,359 --> 00:00:56,159
Oh, so it was the lightning strike

10
00:00:56,159 --> 00:00:57,679
that merged us together.

11
00:00:57,840 --> 00:00:59,320
So in theory...

12
00:00:59,480 --> 00:01:02,240
Another shock should separate us again.

13
00:01:04,600 --> 00:01:06,800
What are you doing? Calm down.

14
00:01:06,840 --> 00:01:07,640
You can do it.

15
00:01:07,640 --> 00:01:09,000
No, I can't.

16
00:01:09,000 --> 00:01:09,840
Yes, you can.

17
00:01:09,840 --> 00:01:11,480
- No, I can't.
- Yes, you can.

18
00:01:11,480 --> 00:01:12,480
Yes!

19
00:01:12,480 --> 00:01:13,160
No!

20
00:01:13,160 --> 00:01:14,190
- Yes, you can.
- I can...

21
00:01:15,239 --> 00:01:16,519
(How dare you betray me.)

22
00:01:24,275 --> 00:01:27,062
Don't think being a cushion helps.

23
00:01:28,840 --> 00:01:30,480
(Could it be that Qiao Nian)

24
00:01:30,750 --> 00:01:32,869
(is really living inside me?)

25
00:01:37,837 --> 00:01:39,925
(Grandpa)

26
00:01:41,959 --> 00:01:42,879
Hello? Grandpa?

27
00:01:43,040 --> 00:01:45,000
Zechen, come home now.

28
00:01:46,120 --> 00:01:48,040
Alright.

29
00:01:48,920 --> 00:01:50,760
This is absolutely outrageous!

30
00:01:51,359 --> 00:01:52,959
How dare they touch Nian.

31
00:01:56,000 --> 00:01:58,280
(It seems only Jiang Zechen can see me.)

32
00:01:58,640 --> 00:02:00,079
(No one else can.)

33
00:02:01,159 --> 00:02:01,959
Grandpa.

34
00:02:06,840 --> 00:02:09,280
Zechen, take a look at this.

35
00:02:10,462 --> 00:02:12,412
(Trading the Qiao Group for her!)

36
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:14,319
(My body?)

37
00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:16,319
(Who did this to me?)

38
00:02:28,719 --> 00:02:30,159
(Aunt Wenjun is very cunning.)

39
00:02:30,159 --> 00:02:32,280
(She won't slip up easily.)

40
00:02:35,400 --> 00:02:37,560
(Duan Yiran isn't that smart.)

41
00:02:37,610 --> 00:02:39,120
(She wears her emotions on her sleeve.)

42
00:02:39,439 --> 00:02:42,199
(Something's off about her.)

43
00:02:43,319 --> 00:02:44,479
(With Qiao Nian gone,)

44
00:02:44,719 --> 00:02:46,199
(Jiang Zechen is totally mine.)

45
00:02:47,560 --> 00:02:48,599
(He's looking at me.)

46
00:02:52,599 --> 00:02:53,560
Jiang Zechen,

47
00:02:55,000 --> 00:02:56,319
are you suspecting me?

48
00:02:56,759 --> 00:02:59,439
I just had a falling out with Qiao Nian.

49
00:03:00,039 --> 00:03:03,240
Why kidnap her and make things worse?

50
00:03:04,520 --> 00:03:05,680
(Like I'd believe that.)

51
00:03:07,919 --> 00:03:08,719
Zechen,

52
00:03:09,919 --> 00:03:11,599
you were with her yesterday.

53
00:03:11,960 --> 00:03:16,159
Did you see the kidnapper?

54
00:03:16,439 --> 00:03:18,520
They wiped yesterday's footage.

55
00:03:18,960 --> 00:03:20,240
There are no leads whatsoever.

56
00:03:21,479 --> 00:03:23,599
Who knows if you're telling the truth?

57
00:03:23,599 --> 00:03:26,140
Maybe you set this whole thing up

58
00:03:26,150 --> 00:03:27,479
to get your hands on Qiao Group.

59
00:03:27,479 --> 00:03:28,280
Aunt Wenjun,

60
00:03:28,919 --> 00:03:31,360
I didn't mean any of that
at yesterday's meeting.

61
00:03:31,840 --> 00:03:33,439
We're on the same side.

62
00:03:35,175 --> 00:03:37,015
I had no reason for this.

63
00:03:40,840 --> 00:03:41,719
Grandpa.

64
00:03:53,599 --> 00:03:54,319
Grandpa,

65
00:03:55,039 --> 00:03:56,039
are you feeling better?

66
00:03:58,840 --> 00:04:00,080
How are you feeling, Grandpa?

67
00:04:01,240 --> 00:04:03,400
Better.

68
00:04:04,360 --> 00:04:07,080
Grandpa, should we
comply with the demands,

69
00:04:07,199 --> 00:04:08,599
mobilize our resources quietly,

70
00:04:08,599 --> 00:04:10,000
and get my body back?

71
00:04:10,039 --> 00:04:10,840
Huh?

72
00:04:11,400 --> 00:04:15,159
Sorry, I meant Nian.

73
00:04:16,079 --> 00:04:16,879
Alright.

74
00:04:17,519 --> 00:04:18,680
Then it's settled.

75
00:04:19,279 --> 00:04:21,759
I'll handle this matter personally.

76
00:04:22,079 --> 00:04:24,040
The rest of you,
go attend to your own affairs.

77
00:04:25,319 --> 00:04:26,160
Go on.

78
00:04:29,000 --> 00:04:30,519
Grandpa, I'll be going now.

79
00:04:30,960 --> 00:04:34,480
(Looking at Zechen feels
just like looking at Qiao Nian.)

80
00:04:35,240 --> 00:04:38,520
(Nian, I will bring you back
no matter what.)

81
00:04:43,040 --> 00:04:44,079
(What is that smell?)

82
00:04:47,360 --> 00:04:49,120
It's so familiar.

83
00:04:52,560 --> 00:04:53,360
Yiran,

84
00:04:55,240 --> 00:04:56,399
what is it, brother-in-law?

85
00:04:56,662 --> 00:04:58,102
That's an unusual perfume.

86
00:04:58,410 --> 00:04:59,279
Where did you get it?

87
00:04:59,510 --> 00:05:01,150
I'd like to get
a bottle for your sister.

88
00:05:01,725 --> 00:05:03,720
This was custom-made for me in France.

89
00:05:04,120 --> 00:05:06,319
If you like it, it's yours.

90
00:05:08,800 --> 00:05:11,240
(He seems off today.)

91
00:05:12,560 --> 00:05:15,162
Hello, Mr. Zhang? What's up?

92
00:05:17,079 --> 00:05:18,720
Don't you dare give it to anyone else.

93
00:05:31,560 --> 00:05:32,240
Weirdo.

94
00:05:38,639 --> 00:05:40,240
What's so special about this perfume?

95
00:05:40,439 --> 00:05:41,879
I just remembered something.

96
00:05:41,879 --> 00:05:43,680
My kidnapper had this exact scent.

97
00:05:44,000 --> 00:05:46,959
You're saying Duan Yiran
sent someone to kidnap you?

98
00:05:47,040 --> 00:05:47,839
Yes.

99
00:05:48,800 --> 00:05:49,839
It was a man.

100
00:05:50,639 --> 00:05:51,439
That's right.

101
00:05:51,959 --> 00:05:54,800
Apart from the two of them,
who else is after Qiao Group?

102
00:05:54,959 --> 00:05:55,800
There's also you.

103
00:05:56,199 --> 00:05:57,000
Me?

104
00:05:58,360 --> 00:06:01,120
Weren't you with them?

105
00:06:01,319 --> 00:06:03,920
Did they not even loop you in?

106
00:06:05,160 --> 00:06:09,439
I was just a puppet on a string.

107
00:06:10,399 --> 00:06:13,959
(I'll use your body to find the truth.)

108
00:06:20,199 --> 00:06:23,000
Mr. Jiang, is our partnership still on?

109
00:06:24,399 --> 00:06:25,199
Of course.

110
00:06:26,920 --> 00:06:30,639
Mind if I ask one more thing?

111
00:06:31,600 --> 00:06:32,199
Go ahead.

112
00:06:32,199 --> 00:06:33,879
Is Qiao Nian with you?

113
00:06:37,040 --> 00:06:37,839
Ms. Qiao,

114
00:06:38,480 --> 00:06:40,399
is there a misunderstanding?

115
00:06:41,800 --> 00:06:43,120
Qiao Nian has gone missing.

116
00:06:46,560 --> 00:06:48,120
Isn't that rather convenient?

117
00:06:48,680 --> 00:06:51,879
If you take control of Qiao Group,

118
00:06:52,399 --> 00:06:54,680
our partnership will be secured.

119
00:06:56,240 --> 00:06:58,040
(Doesn't seem like he's behind it.)

120
00:06:59,560 --> 00:07:00,720
Then I'll take my leave.

121
00:07:00,879 --> 00:07:01,680
Sure.

122
00:07:07,800 --> 00:07:10,639
Keep playing your little games,

123
00:07:11,319 --> 00:07:13,160
and I'll be the one to spring the trap.

124
00:07:30,839 --> 00:07:31,920
(With Qiao Nian gone,)

125
00:07:32,360 --> 00:07:35,959
(it's all mine for the taking.)

126
00:07:50,959 --> 00:07:52,279
(Let's start with Duan Yiran.)

127
00:07:53,519 --> 00:07:56,040
Miss Duan, here's her report.

128
00:08:00,620 --> 00:08:01,839
I can't make sense of all this.

129
00:08:01,879 --> 00:08:03,800
Dr. Li, just tell me the conclusion.

130
00:08:04,000 --> 00:08:05,720
All her vital indicators are normal.

131
00:08:05,730 --> 00:08:07,200
She just can't wake up at the moment.

132
00:08:07,319 --> 00:08:09,199
It's likely due to brain damage.

133
00:08:15,600 --> 00:08:16,399
Good day.

134
00:08:25,362 --> 00:08:26,687
(I promise to keep her safe.)

135
00:08:28,560 --> 00:08:31,000
The old man's been taken care of.

136
00:08:31,839 --> 00:08:32,639
Hmm.

137
00:08:37,399 --> 00:08:38,200
Master.

138
00:08:47,000 --> 00:08:50,159
Guys who are this good-looking

139
00:08:50,679 --> 00:08:54,159
and capable are hard to find.

140
00:09:01,200 --> 00:09:02,320
So about our marriage...

141
00:09:05,440 --> 00:09:06,960
The timing isn't right yet.

142
00:09:07,799 --> 00:09:11,480
Once we take the Group,
we'll make it official.

143
00:09:11,875 --> 00:09:16,837
Then, everything I have will be yours.

144
00:09:19,840 --> 00:09:20,639
Hey.

145
00:09:49,450 --> 00:09:51,490
(Quick, record Duan Yiran's confession.)

146
00:09:58,759 --> 00:10:00,879
(Why does this feel so strange?)

147
00:10:07,900 --> 00:10:08,699
Sorry.

148
00:10:09,900 --> 00:10:12,540
(Jiang Zechen, you're not kissing me!)

149
00:10:20,812 --> 00:10:23,293
I think we've been spotted.

150
00:10:39,200 --> 00:10:39,925
Qiao Nian.

151
00:10:42,762 --> 00:10:43,561
Qiao Nian,

152
00:10:44,575 --> 00:10:45,815
are you alright?

153
00:10:45,919 --> 00:10:46,720
Zechen,

154
00:10:47,679 --> 00:10:48,960
I feel terrible.

155
00:10:49,840 --> 00:10:51,519
I think I might not make it.

156
00:10:52,000 --> 00:10:54,000
No, you'll be fine.

157
00:10:55,960 --> 00:10:57,399
I checked online.

158
00:10:57,762 --> 00:11:01,360
Apparently, the body
only lasts seven days.

159
00:11:02,375 --> 00:11:04,375
Am I really going to die?

160
00:11:04,480 --> 00:11:06,120
No, you won't.

161
00:11:06,440 --> 00:11:08,960
You'll be fine. Everything will be fine.

162
00:11:09,325 --> 00:11:13,962
(Life countdown: 6 days)

163
00:11:19,080 --> 00:11:20,320
Are you feeling any better?

164
00:11:20,639 --> 00:11:22,399
I think I'm much better.

165
00:11:26,720 --> 00:11:27,639
Where's Duan Yiran?

166
00:11:28,320 --> 00:11:29,840
Why is Bai Niansheng the only one here?

167
00:11:30,600 --> 00:11:31,399
Hmm?

168
00:11:31,960 --> 00:11:33,360
That's Duan Yiran's car.

169
00:11:33,360 --> 00:11:34,120
Oh?

170
00:11:37,120 --> 00:11:40,639
Let's follow the lead
and see where it goes.

171
00:11:41,887 --> 00:11:42,686
Yes!

172
00:11:46,312 --> 00:11:48,512
(Bai Niansheng's meeting
Duan Yiran in secret.)

173
00:11:59,320 --> 00:12:00,639
(Let me play along with you.)

174
00:12:08,000 --> 00:12:10,000
He's been leading us around in circles.

175
00:12:10,925 --> 00:12:12,724
He must have spotted us.

176
00:12:17,600 --> 00:12:19,000
He's getting out of the car.

177
00:12:30,220 --> 00:12:31,500
What a coincidence, Mr. Jiang.

178
00:12:33,759 --> 00:12:35,200
Indeed.

179
00:12:35,360 --> 00:12:36,600
What do you think you're doing?

180
00:12:36,600 --> 00:12:37,600
Let go of me right now.

181
00:12:37,720 --> 00:12:38,879
Mr. Bai,

182
00:12:40,080 --> 00:12:42,200
as Mr. Qiao's personal assistant,

183
00:12:43,000 --> 00:12:45,440
sneaking around with Miss Duan?

184
00:12:47,559 --> 00:12:49,279
I'm sure you don't want this to blow up.

185
00:12:49,800 --> 00:12:51,080
I was wrong, Mr. Jiang.

186
00:12:51,440 --> 00:12:52,559
I admit it, alright?

187
00:12:52,700 --> 00:12:53,759
I'll do whatever you ask.

188
00:12:54,600 --> 00:12:57,080
Where have you hidden Qiao Nian's body?

189
00:12:57,799 --> 00:12:58,399
That's right!

190
00:12:58,399 --> 00:13:00,159
Where have you hidden my body?

191
00:13:00,559 --> 00:13:01,759
What are you talking about?

192
00:13:01,759 --> 00:13:03,159
I have no idea what you mean.

193
00:13:05,039 --> 00:13:05,840
Mr. Bai,

194
00:13:07,279 --> 00:13:09,399
On the night you kidnapped Qiao Nian,

195
00:13:10,600 --> 00:13:13,039
you had a very distinctive scent on you.

196
00:13:13,687 --> 00:13:16,400
(Zechen, use him to find my body.)

197
00:13:17,879 --> 00:13:19,600
It was this one, wasn't it?

198
00:13:26,987 --> 00:13:28,426
I've got my eye on you.

199
00:13:32,519 --> 00:13:35,639
Nice move. Luring the snake out.

200
00:13:36,240 --> 00:13:38,720
One way or another, they'll slip up.

201
00:13:44,240 --> 00:13:45,919
Qiao Nian!

202
00:13:46,360 --> 00:13:47,879
Why does everything go to you?

203
00:13:49,262 --> 00:13:50,381
If it weren't for you,

204
00:13:51,125 --> 00:13:53,164
I would be the apple of their eye.

205
00:13:54,360 --> 00:13:56,159
You stole everything from me!

206
00:13:57,875 --> 00:13:58,835
Otherwise,

207
00:14:00,399 --> 00:14:02,279
Mom would've given me a second look.

208
00:14:10,700 --> 00:14:13,575
(Bai Niansheng)

209
00:14:15,399 --> 00:14:16,200
Hello?

210
00:14:16,240 --> 00:14:18,360
Miss Duan, I've been found out.

211
00:14:18,720 --> 00:14:21,360
We need to deal with
Jiang Zechen quickly.

212
00:14:22,200 --> 00:14:23,120
Don't panic.

213
00:14:23,720 --> 00:14:24,519
I have a plan.

214
00:14:28,000 --> 00:14:31,080
Yiran, my darling girl.

215
00:14:39,840 --> 00:14:42,320
Mom, what are you doing here?

216
00:14:42,440 --> 00:14:43,639
Just here to see you.

217
00:14:46,039 --> 00:14:48,360
You don't look so well.

218
00:14:48,720 --> 00:14:49,519
Oh?

219
00:14:50,159 --> 00:14:51,730
I probably didn't sleep well last night.

220
00:14:53,320 --> 00:14:55,679
Mom, I just got some Danish king salmon.

221
00:14:55,840 --> 00:14:56,879
Let's try it.

222
00:14:57,919 --> 00:14:59,480
(Something doesn't feel right here.)

223
00:15:11,080 --> 00:15:12,679
Why is he sneaking around?

224
00:15:12,679 --> 00:15:13,679
What's he up to?

225
00:15:21,000 --> 00:15:22,480
That wretched Qiao Nian.

226
00:15:25,399 --> 00:15:27,480
Duan Yiran is truly heartless.

227
00:15:44,879 --> 00:15:45,679
It's a trap!

228
00:15:46,120 --> 00:15:46,919
Stop right there!

229
00:15:47,480 --> 00:15:48,279
Stop!

230
00:15:48,279 --> 00:15:49,080
Don't run!

231
00:15:49,279 --> 00:15:50,080
Don't run!

232
00:15:50,840 --> 00:15:51,639
Don't run!

233
00:16:00,000 --> 00:16:00,799
Are you okay?

234
00:16:00,840 --> 00:16:01,679
That hurts!

235
00:16:08,687 --> 00:16:09,317
Stay back!

236
00:16:09,850 --> 00:16:12,325
Ouch, that really hurts!

237
00:16:12,399 --> 00:16:13,600
What's wrong with this guy?

238
00:16:13,600 --> 00:16:15,120
He's bleeding, yet he doesn't flinch.

239
00:16:21,240 --> 00:16:22,200
I'm bleeding.

240
00:16:22,340 --> 00:16:23,360
Why don't I feel any pain?

241
00:16:23,639 --> 00:16:24,639
I feel it!

242
00:16:28,080 --> 00:16:30,000
(How dare you touch my wife!)

243
00:16:30,120 --> 00:16:31,600
(Why is he talking to himself?)

244
00:16:31,600 --> 00:16:32,600
(Freak.)

245
00:16:34,039 --> 00:16:35,840
How dare you touch my wife?

246
00:16:41,240 --> 00:16:47,200
♪So many words unsaid,
the deeper we fall, the more we fear♪

247
00:16:47,480 --> 00:16:55,090
♪Fate like a gamble,
locking us inside its game♪

248
00:16:55,140 --> 00:16:58,920
♪Hearts at play, truth and lies,
who could ever know♪

249
00:16:59,440 --> 00:17:02,720
♪Where this ends♪

250
00:17:02,720 --> 00:17:10,000
♪I try to walk away,
yet still step into the fire♪

251
00:17:10,000 --> 00:17:14,340
♪Your heartbeat pulls me under,
and I lose myself♪

252
00:17:14,380 --> 00:17:17,460
♪Love turns into pain♪

253
00:17:17,530 --> 00:17:21,650
♪Words betray us
until our eyes burn red♪

254
00:17:21,800 --> 00:17:25,290
♪Yet I still want you close♪

255
00:17:25,290 --> 00:17:29,450
♪Your tide breaks me,
and I fall for you again♪

256
00:17:29,450 --> 00:17:32,760
♪Even if love becomes nothing♪

257
00:17:32,760 --> 00:17:37,340
♪When love and hate fade
into the crowd and the ice melts♪

258
00:17:37,340 --> 00:17:43,640
♪Does it mean we could meet again?♪

259
00:17:44,240 --> 00:17:48,430
♪Your heartbeat pulls me under,
and I lose myself♪

260
